{"tid":313142,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺啲毒撚都係一式咁既頭 配副黑框眼鏡","createTime":"2017-07-08T05:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T08:30:36.000Z","uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43aad83585f374399a8c3a4ff88cd035d6b674cd","tid":313142,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/08/134814_b711c5be21858ce83646e30baf43b3b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F08%2F134814_b711c5be21858ce83646e30baf43b3b1.jpg&h=51941df5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瘦到得排骨 仲要柒個金色既頭 真係忍唔住笑<br />\n<br />\n正正常"},{"pid":"1eac60c0a8ded113f637c7ef9874eb44a4d8a84a","tid":313142,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正正常常咁留個長頭髮都冇乜野<br />\n係要留撻死人陰 遮住個樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote>"},{"pid":"5857efaabc326c1362b32942c48780050d6e0adc","tid":313142,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:36:02.000Z","msg":"巴絲們<br />\n<br />\n大熱天時 緊係想食啲野 cool down 個人<br />\n雪糕就就手 又多選擇 隨時係街買到 <br />\n但係食得多有啲厭<br />\n<br />\n記得舊年定前年哈根大有柚子雪芭<br />\n喂 正喎 涷涷地又唔太heavy <br />\n不過之後好似唔見有<br />\n<br />\n再周圍搵邊度有 可惜搵到好食既唔多<br />\n想搵下邊度有好味既雪芭<br />\n<br />\n謝謝"},{"pid":"205b4d729efeb4da423b9d6af2b4c489c96918c2","tid":313142,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T07:46:11.000Z","msg":"右邊好日系風格"},{"pid":"5d578e27e2644278b2e3aa6dabddea445f86a715","tid":313142,"uid":25221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d90bb8236273475b865d3765dfa52ac126f637d4","tid":313142,"uid":103380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T07:54:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>右邊好日系風格</blockquote><br />\n真係架仔先carry到<br />\n<br />\n香港啲毒撚